casebody.data:
Christopher DESMOND, petitioner,
v.
DELAWARE. No. 13-7656. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014. Case below, 74 A.3d 653 . Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Delaware dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
